  "Ryan Rollins": "Rollins didn't suit up for Sunday's 127-113 loss to the Clippers before returning for Tuesday's win over the Dallas Mavericks. He logged 36 minutes, finishing with 24 points, seven rebounds, nine assists and one steal across 36 minutes. However, the 23-year-old won't play in the second of a back-to-back. With Kevin Porter (knee) out as well, the Bucks will lean on Andre Jackson, AJ Green, and Gary Trent to handle most of the work in the backcourt.",
