  "Gary Trent Jr.": "Trent checked out with 4:32 remaining in the opening quarter and won't return due to the hip injury. His next opportunity to play will come Friday against Boston. The Bucks have just seven players available for the remainder of Wednesday's game, so Cormac Ryan and Andre Jackson will likely help pick up the slack.",
  "Thanasis Antetokounmpo": "The veteran forward will miss his fourth straight game and remains without a timetable to return. His next chance to play comes Friday against Boston.",
